@startuml notifications-sw-state
' Context: notifications (service worker)
' Contract: docs/specs/contracts/push-payload.md
' SDD: SURF-NOTIFICATIONS-005–008
' Revision: 2026-07-18

title Notifications — service worker state machine

state Waiting
state SuppressionReady : suppressionState in RAM
state NotificationShown

[*] --> Waiting

Waiting --> SuppressionReady : alfred_push_suppression\n/ applySuppressionState

SuppressionReady --> SuppressionReady : alfred_push_suppression\n/ applySuppressionState

SuppressionReady --> Waiting : push event\n[shouldSuppress]\n/ PushNotificationSuppressed
SuppressionReady --> NotificationShown : push event\n[!shouldSuppress, payload valido]\n/ showNotification

NotificationShown --> SuppressionReady : notificationclick\n/ OpenFromPushTap

note right of SuppressionReady
  shouldSuppress quando:
  appVisible && focusUserId == owner
  && activePeerProfileId == peer
end note

@enduml
